block.info: 1) A Challenge to everything we know: Peak Oil/Gas and Climate ChangeA quick run down of some of the core ideas and concepts behind these threats to industrial society and the human species as a whole.2) A Hacker's view of our choices and our role in the process of changeIf Climate change and Peaking fossil fuel production pose threats to human society, how can hackers help to make the change to a more sustainable way of being less traumatic. Does the future have a place for the technology abusers and tweakers?3) One Hacker's personal recollection of a trip into one possible futureI had the chance to go to Kenya's border with Somalia with the UN aid effort in 2006. In this place many of the catastrophes that are foretold for the rest of the world have already happened, with governmental collapse, lack of resources and war. Rather weirdly, many many people displayed all kinds of traits one would expect to find in Hackers... /
